  <brief_title>PET/CT Guided Fulvestrant Therapy for Patients With Recurrent or Metastatic Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Clinical Trial to Evaluate 18F-Fluoroestradiol Positron Emission Tomography / Computerized Tomography (PET/CT) Guided Fulvestrant Therapy for Patients With Recurrent or Metastatic Breast Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
